=== 大榮華酒樓 ===
大榮華酒樓於1975年開設，1998年12月重開，主要供應[[圍頭菜|圍頭菜]]，並由有「食神」之稱的廚師[[梁文韜|梁文韜]]主理。著名菜色有懷舊菜[[雞蛋|雞蛋]][[蒸焗魚腸|焗魚腸]]、白水浸[[烏頭|烏頭]]、炒[[粉絲|長遠]]，拌以[[頭抽|頭抽]]及[[豬油|豬油]]的[[豬油拌飯|缽仔蒸飯]]、奶黃[[馬拉糕|馬拉糕]]，及[[臘腸卷|臘腸卷]]等懷舊[[點心|點心]]。2006年9月，大榮華酒樓於[[九龍灣|九龍灣]][[其士商業中心|其士商業中心]]開設九龍首家分店。於2011年4月將[[灣仔|灣仔]]榮華酒樓改為大榮華圍村菜。

===榮華月餅===
榮華月餅为该集团的招牌产品，其广告语“清香嫩滑，零舍不同”、“行船争解缆，月饼我卖先”已沿用数十年<ref name=nfdsb>{{Cite web|url =http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/D/html/2014-08/19/content_3298204.htm?div=4|title =64年的新蜕变：香港荣华集团历史老品牌国际化|author =黄丽嫦|date =2014-08-19|publisher =南方都市报|language =|accessdate =quote =|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005152401/http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/D/html/2014-08/19/content_3298204.htm?div=4|archive-date =2017-10-05|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。由于荣华于每年端午节之后便开始销售月饼，较其他品牌早，所以有“行船争解缆，月饼我卖先”的说法<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2017-10-02/doc-ifymkwwk7895511.shtml|title =香港重视月饼浪费现象 简装、慈善促环保|author =殷晓媛|date =2017-10-02|publisher =新华社|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2019-05-20|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190520235801/http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2017-10-02/doc-ifymkwwk7895511.shtml|dead-url =no}}</ref>。

==商标纠纷==
{{main|荣华品牌之争}}
[[File:Wing_Wah_mooncakes_displayed_at_counter_of_Jiuguang_Department_Store,_Suzhou.jpg|缩略图]]
荣华月饼在1979年便进入中国内地市场<ref name=sina>{{Cite web|url = http://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/20120409/145411777500.shtml|title = 14年粤港荣华月饼商标案最后对决 最高法近期再审|author = 吕卫红|date = 2012-04-09|publisher = 正义网|language = |accessdate = |quote = |archive-date = 2017-10-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171005201841/http://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/20120409/145411777500.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url =http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/D/html/2014-08/19/content_3298204.htm?div=4|title =64年的新蜕变：香港荣华集团历史老品牌国际化|author =黄丽嫦|date =2014-08-19|publisher =南方都市报|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005152401/http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/D/html/2014-08/19/content_3298204.htm?div=4|archive-date =2017-10-05|dead-url =yes}}</ref>，由於未為意兩地商標法不同，香港荣华没有及時註冊商標<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20130730/00407_047.html|title =香港榮華商標維權 官司擾攘15年終獲勝|author =|date =2013-07-30|publisher =太阳报|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2013-08-04|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130804012221/http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20130730/00407_047.html|dead-url =no}}</ref>。1995年-1996年，香港荣华冠名赞助[[新华社香港分社|新华社香港分社]]主办的[[世界女排大奖赛|世界女排大奖赛]]，由于多场赛事通过中国内地多家电视台转播，荣华月饼在中国内地的知名度迅速提升<ref name=sina/>。然而，香港荣华的“荣华”商标并未在中国内地成功注册<ref name=sina/>。

另一方面，在1997年，当时名为“顺德市勒流镇苏氏荣华食品厂”（即现在的[[苏氏荣华食品|苏氏荣华食品]]）生产了以“花好月圆”做外包装盒的月饼，标志与香港荣华一样，使用“荣华月饼”字样，此举激怒了香港荣华和东莞荣华。为此，香港荣华将苏氏荣华告上法庭，而双方也陷入了休止的商标权诉讼中<ref name=sina/>。据统计，双方之间的相关诉讼多达58起，相关案件的诉讼费超过1000万元<ref name=15years>{{Cite web|url =http://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/20130730/113616286368.shtml|title =粤港荣华品牌之争持续15年：仍有六场官司要打|author =|date =2013-07-30|publisher =中新网|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2017-10-05|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005152145/http://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/20130730/113616286368.shtml|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name=people>{{Cite web|url =http://ip.people.com.cn/n/2013/0129/c136655-20356956.html|title =谁的月饼?"香港荣华"VS"顺德荣华"15载争名又开战|author =周伟良|date =2013-01-29|publisher =广州日报|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2017-10-05|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005152113/http://ip.people.com.cn/n/2013/0129/c136655-20356956.html|dead-url =no}}</ref>。

在持续性的商标诉讼期间，为了避免苏氏荣华再指香港荣华侵權，香港荣华先后推出了「元朗榮華」、「WING WAH」新品牌月饼<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2013-06-28/753756.html|title =纠缠商标战多年 香港荣华推“元朗荣华”谋多元化|author =|date =2013-06-28|publisher =每经网|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2017-10-05|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005151420/http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2013-06-28/753756.html|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url =http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130730/18355686|title =港推「元朗榮華」月餅免被順德榮華指侵權|author =|date =2013-07-30|publisher =香港苹果日报|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2017-10-05|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005151847/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130730/18355686|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name=tkb>{{Cite web|url =http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2014/0709/2586475.html|title =榮華月餅內地改名Wing Wah|author =|date =2014-07-09|publisher =大公报|language =|accessdate =|quote =|archive-date =2017-10-05|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171005152131/http://news.takungpao.com.hk/paper/q/2014/0709/2586475.html|dead-url =no}}</ref>，及后一直使用至今<ref name=tkb/>。

